Gliese
Fleet

Name: d_tokki
Text: Intelligence supremacist. Great at acting.

Name: d_tokki
Text: From the super-class "Gliese Mobile Fleet" state.

Name: d_tokki
Text: Assigned male gender at birth; identifies as non-binary.

Name: d_tokki
Text: Communicative, but not so much verbally.

Name: d_tokki
Text: Was a high school student in Gliese.

Name: d_tokki
Text: Owner of the "Silver Key" by birthright.

Name: d_tokki
Text: Three Sizes 7

Name: t_aisatu
Text:
I'm {0}. Remember it.
It's no exaggeration to say that the universe was born with me.

Name: t_suspect
Text:
You're beyond redemption, {0}.
I sense no intelligence in you. Not in the slightest.

Name: t_suspect
Text:
{0}, you're casting the discussion into confusion.
Hmph... I'll rephrase it in a way even you can understand.
{0}, you're annoying. Shut up.

Name: t_suspect
Text:
Why do you all trust {0}?
I'll never understand how commoners think...

Name: t_suspect
Text: Pressing on those who stay suspiciously quiet, like {0}, sounds prudent.

Name: t_suspect
Text:
Thinking logically, we should probably be suspecting...
{0}, I feel.

Name: t_suspect
Text: {0}, are you hiding something?

Name: t_suspect
Text:
OK, this is where my aliance with {0} ends.
In case it wasn't obvious, {0} doesn't deserve our trust.

Name: t_suspect
Text:
So last night, it was {1} who disappeared.
Well then, haha, isn't it clear whom we should suspect?
{0}. You.

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
Hm... I guess {0} is irredeemable after all.
No real purpose left to serve for us.

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
Shut up, {0}.
You're only serving to exacerbate my dislike of you.

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
{0} isn't worthy of our trust.
I tried trusting {0}, but it turned out to be completely pointless.

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
{0}. Speak up more, and show your true self.
I have high expectations of you.

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
OK, I'm going to suspect {0}.
I mean, logically, it only makes sense, right?

Name: t_suspect_r
Text:
You know what? I trust {0}.
So to make a change in the situation, I'm gonna try doubting {0} now.

Name: t_suspect_add
Text:
{0} seems pretty suspicious, right?
Just sort of too pathetic to be an actual human.

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
I like how this is going...
I'd like to see {0} go into cold sleep.

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
Haha, how annoying, and suspicious to boot.
What are you doing, {0}? Are you up for election or something?

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
Huh... That's not bad, {1}.
I think we should start focusing on {0} about now.

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
Just what are you hiding, {0}?
You don't actually HAVE to answer, you know.

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
It's clear what's going on here.
Is there really anyone who doesn't suspect {0}?

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text:
So I see I wasn't the only one suspecting {0}.
You're starting to come around, I guess.

Name: t_suspect_t0
Text: Of course suspicions arise. {0} is just so untrustworthy.

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text:
So basically, {1} dislikes - and therefore wants to freeze - {0}.
Haha. Well, why not?

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text:
{0} screwed up.
They've lost my trust.

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text:
Heh, so now we're going to jump on {0}?
Sure, I'll take that ride, haha.

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text: It's only natural to cast doubt upon those who keep quiet.

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text: Huh, a rational opinion. How rare. I support it.

Name: t_suspect_t1
Text:
Hey, you sure have become unpopular, {0}.
Of course no one would trust someone like you!

Name: t_suspected0
Text: Huh... Are you really doubting me?

Name: t_suspected0
Text:
Resorting to ad hominem attacks due to lack of actual reason?
What kind of idiot lets that sort of thing shake them up?

Name: t_hanron0
Text:
{0} isn't the one we should be suspecting right now.
I mean, come on... really?

Name: t_hanron0
Text:
You just don't get it, do you?
This whole trend of casting doubt on {0} is clearly some kind of ploy.

Name: t_hanron1
Text:
I support {0}.
Seeing {0} like this is just too pathetic. Haha!

Name: t_hanron_t0
Text: I say {0} is alright. Aren't I such a good person? Ahaha!

Name: t_hanron_t1
Text: If {1} says one thing, I think we should assume the opposite is true.

Name: t_trust
Text:
{0}, you're actually not so bad.
I actually think I can trust you.

Name: t_trust
Text: Well, let me just say I feel we can trust {0}.

Name: t_trust
Text: Are there really any idiots here who would suspect {0}?

Name: t_trust_r
Text:
Personally, I want to avoid sending {0} off to cold sleep.
I like watching {0} squirm and fight.

Name: t_trust_r
Text:
As for whom we should allow to remain...
Unfortunately, {0} just seems to trustworthy to let go.

Name: t_trust_r
Text:
I've actually been observing {0} for awhile now.
{0} is clear, and deserves our trust.

Name: t_trust_t0
Text: I agree. {0} should be allowed to remain.

Name: t_trust_t1
Text: I agree. There are others we should be attacking before {0}.

Name: t_trusted0
Text:
Huh... Are you trying to form an alliance with me?
What a wise choice, ahahaha!

Name: t_thanron0
Text: I don't have a single reason to trust {0}, personally.

Name: t_thanron1
Text:
Hmph, looks like {0} and {1} are colluding.
I don't trust people like that.

Name: t_thanron_t0
Text: Just what is "trust", anyway? Some sort of religious term?

Name: t_thanron_t1
Text: Do you think I'd have a reason to follow {0}?

Name: t_hosho
Text: It's obvious, but I feel it's safe to say that {0} is the {1}.

Name: t_hosho
Text:
OK, there's no longer any need to doubt {0}.
As anticlimactic as it may be, {0} is clearly human.

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
OK, you must all have noticed by now, right?
{0} couldn't possibly be {1}.

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
{0} is the {1}.
Hah, did you think I would somehow miss this?

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
Wow, to think that {0} is the {1}.
Hey, {0}. I don't get it myself, but is it fun to live according to an ideology?

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
{0}... Just what are you?
A {1}...? Attempting to throw the universe into chaos...?

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
Haha, you've screwed up, {0}.
Your argument makes no sense.
You're screwed now. Ahahahaha!

Name: t_hosho_enemy
Text:
Aa, I see. So, {0}, then.
So you're an AC Follower, or a Bug.

Name: t_hosho_miss
Text:
You're trying so hard, {0}.
But, you're all wrong, haha.

Name: t_hosho_miss
Text:
Yeah, we already know that, you know?
{0}, stop making useless comments.
You yourself are starting to feel useless.

Name: t_hosho_get
Text:
Did you all really just realize now that I'm {1}?
Haha, no, of course not, right?

Name: t_hosho_get
Text:
I seem to have underestimated you all. And now, here we are.
I'm not angry, I know I have to calmly accept my fate now.
I admire how deftly you entrapped me, actually.

Name: t_tohyo_go
Text:
There's no more point in debating.
I think we should get on with the vote.

Name: t_tohyo_mae
Text:
Let's stop debating and vote.
Hooray for democracy, haha.

Name: t_tohyo_sai
Text:
So we have the results...
We'll vote again between {0}.

Name: t_shokei
Text:
So I'm gone, then, hm? You're all beyond salvation.
Like a bunch of lemmings. But that's fine with me. I don't care.
I'll accept my death sentence. In fact, I welcome it.

Name: t_shokei
Text: Hmph...!

Name: t_wakare
Text: {0}, I'm disappointed in you.

Name: t_karare
Text:
You're the {0}? And you've come to eliminate me?
Aha, this is amusing. Ahahahahahaha...

Name: t_imjinro
Text:
That's right, I'm {0}. It's obvious, isn't it?
Me! Did you really think I was some stupid human?!
You really are stupid! Ahahahahahahahaaaaa!

Name: t_shori
Text:
So it seems I've beaten the {0}.
Or rather, we've beaten them, I guess...

Name: t_tohyo_kurikaeshi
Text:
Oh come on...
You aren't all stupid enough to keep redoing the vote, are you?

Name: t_tohyo_jeno
Text:
So, we just need to put all of the candidates into cold sleep, right?
Suspicion itself is a sin, after all. This is how we royalty handle such matters, haha.

Name: t_tohyo_alive
Text:
Hmph, {0}...
I think we should keep them all here, strength in numbers and all...

Name: t_tohyo_jeno_ok
Text:
Swift and decisive.
I'm behind it. Let us put them all into cold sleep.

Name: t_tohyo_jeno_ng
Text: I object. I don't like the idea, nor that it was YOUR idea.

Name: t_tohyo_alive_ok
Text: OK, fine, let them all stay, then.

Name: t_tohyo_alive_ng
Text: I don't like it.

Name: t_tohyo_jeno_kettei
Text:
OK... Everyone is off to cold sleep!
What, isn't this clearly the answer?

Name: t_tohyo_alive_kettei
Text:
OK... So we let them all remain.
I'll be off now. I'm busy.

Name: t_tohyo_hitei
Text:
Hm... So you reject my proposal.
Well then, do any of you have a better idea?

Name: t_tohyo_dame
Text:
Haah... Let's just give up for tonight.
I'm... getting sleepy...

Name: t_tohyo_dame
Text:
Let's leave it here for tonight...
Nothing good is going to come of this anyway.

Name: t_co
Text: dammy

Name: t_co
Text:
I'm the {0}. Give me 16 hours and I'll find the Gnosia.
All you need to do is get rid of them once they're found.

Name: t_co
Text:
You're all so lucky that I'm the {0}, huh?
I can tell who is or isn't Gnosia, so keep freezing anyone suspicious.

Name: t_co
Text:
I'm a {0}. I'm sure fools can't tell the difference, though.
Battle requires brains, not brawn.

Name: t_co
Text:
I'm sure you'd all like to get rid of me. Haha, well too bad!
When we last docked, I remained here on the ship.
So there's no way I could've been infected by the Gnosia.

Name: t_co
Text: dammy

Name: t_co
Text: dammy

Name: t_co
Text: dammy

Name: t_co
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text:
I'm the {0}. I kept quiet about it as a strategy.
And {1} is Gnosia. Do away with them quickly.

Name: t_co_find
Text:
There was an idiot Gnosia in cold sleep. It was {1}.
That's right, I was the {0}.

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_find
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text:
Hm... So {1} isn't human.
It's simple. I know this because I'm the only true {0} here.

Name: t_co_taiko
Text:
You've made a bad call, {1}.
Making an enemy of me, the only true {0} on this ship.

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text:
I can confirm. {1} and I remained here on the ship.
So our alibis are solid! Haha!

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_taiko
Text: dammy

Name: t_co_req
Text: I think the {0} should make themselves known now.

Name: t_co_after
Text:
{1} is the {0}?
Let's just hope they're not in over their head.

Name: t_co_after
Text:
I just want to say that among {1}, one of them is a fake.
I mean, they may both be fakes, actually. We'll see.

Name: t_co_after
Text:
Ahaha! A war over the position of {0}!
Thanks, all of you.
This will help weed out the Gnosia.

Name: t_uranai_o
Text: Wow, you're trying to discredit my research?

Name: t_uranai_s
Text: Allow me to report my findings.

Name: t_uranai_b
Text: Hmph. Well, next is my own report.

Name: t_uranai_t
Text: Put simply, {1} is {0}. Ahaha!

Name: t_uranai_f
Text:
{1} wasn't {0}. Haah...
{1} is suspicious, anyway, you think about it.

Name: t_uranai_n
Text: Further investigation would just be pointless, wouldn't it?

Name: t_reibai_s
Text: I've already examined those in cold sleep.

Name: t_reibai_t
Text:
{1} {3} {0}. That much is clear.
Let's keep it up with the cold sleep.

Name: t_reibai_f
Text:
{1} isn't {0}, just a normal human.
I had expected more.

Name: t_reibai_ft
Text:
Among {1}, {2} {4} {0}.
Not bad, I guess.

Name: t_reibai_ff
Text: {1} were all normal humans. Hah, we were way off.

Name: t_houkoku_s
Text: Hmph. Well, I guess I believe you. I got the same results myself.

Name: t_houkoku_w
Text: Haha, no. The fake has shown their hand!

Name: t_okuyami
Text:
Another one was taken out?
Our ability to fight is being gradually whittled down...

Name: t_okuyami_n
Text:
Ahahaha, the Gnosia is pretty stupid, I see.
Wasting an opportunity to attack like that.

Name: t_okuyami_f
Text:
The victims were {0}? Hm...
It's simple. One of them was a Bug.

Name: t_houkoku_req
Text: Someone has a report to give, right? Hurry it up.

Name: t_houkoku_not
Text:
OK, let's get the debate going.
I'm sure {0} will get plenty of votes, dodging the report like that.

Name: t_skill_sayNingen
Text:
Hm, so you want to make the fake lie, huh?
I don't care much for these tactics.
Oh well, either way I'm human, so I don't care.

Name: t_skill_sayNingen
Text:
I refuse.
I don't like these antiquated tactics.

Name: t_skill_zatsudan
Text:
So, you're a foodie, are you?
Supplements are sufficient for both essential nutrients and appetite control, aren't they?

Name: t_skill_zatsudan
Text:
The mental function of the mating instinct has long been understood.
IS there something about it you don't understand?

Name: t_skill_zatsudan
Text:
Recently, I feel as though someone is watching me in the shower.
It's more creepy than scary, really.

Name: t_skill_zatsudan
Text:
I don't like this...
{0}. You simply don't like me, do you?

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
I came up with an idea even all of you could understand.
It's simple. All who claimed to be the {0} go into cold sleep.
It's clear that there's a fake among them, right?

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
Not bad. So a sacrifice, basically?
The true {0} and the fakes will all sleep together.
We should build them a monument.

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
Put those who claimed to be the {0} into cold sleep... And then what?
That won't work, {1}. You have no vision.

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
Why don't we just leave them alone?
The fake will make a mistake at some point anyway.

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
Ahaha, the next vote will be a test of intelligence.
Anyone with a functioning brain would vote for them, after all.

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
Well, voting for them would be best at this point, I guess.
Ignore my plan and do as you like, if you want to die.

Name: t_skill_roller
Text:
This is pointless. Why not put them all into cold sleep?
I doubt any of you could find another way to find the fake anyway.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Let's just put {0} into cold sleep.
Didn't you hear {1}'s assessment? {0} is Gnosia.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Can we just hurry up and put {0} into cold sleep?
Were you not listening? {0} is Gnosia.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Seriously, just hurry up and put {0} into cold sleep.
They're a fake, after all.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Are you memories getting mixed up, {1}?
I didn't hear any report saying that.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
We don't have enough evidence for the rest anyway.
So how about we just vote for {0}?

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Ahahahaha, so is this what's known as mob rule?
But {1}, are you really that much of an instigator?

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text:
Let's stop this, it's wasteful.
I mean, I won't miss {0}, but I don't like seeing a turn to attack go to waste.

Name: t_skill_doTohyo
Text: Haha. This is just stupid.

Name: t_skill_dontTohyo
Text:
You don't all actually plan on voting for {0}, do you?
We don't have anyone that dumb on this ship, do we?

Name: t_skill_dontTohyo
Text:
I don't need {1} to tell me that.
Not even a monkey would be dumb enough to vote for {0}.

Name: t_skill_dontTohyo
Text:
So {1} is trying to tamper with the vote, hm?
Hah, there's obviously no way I'm going to allow this.

Name: t_skill_dontTohyo
Text: Hah, I don't take orders from {1}.

Name: t_skill_kyoryoku
Text:
So, you want to form an alliance, hm?
Ahaha, how surprisingly clever of you to choose me, {0}.
Alright, I guess I'll allow it.

Name: t_skill_kyoryoku
Text:
{0}, even if I were to align myself with you,
what merit would be in it for me?
None whatsoever.

Name: t_skill_t_kyakushoku
Text:
{1}. Just what were you doing last night?
Haha, you don't have to answer. I already know what you are.

Name: t_skill_t_kyakushoku
Text:
Yes, {0}.
The kind of commoners who would seek to freeze {1} should be done away with.

Name: t_skill_t_kyakushoku
Text:
Hah, what a joke.
If {2} wasn't against it, I would be anyway.
Is it even worth listening to what {0} has to say?

Name: t_skill_t_kyakushoku
Text:
Exactly.
Voting for {1} in this situation would only benefit the enemy.

Name: t_skill_h_hangeki
Text:
Hah, trying to attack me in desperation, are you?
It's pointless. It's clear that {0} is more suspicious than I am.

Name: t_skill_h_help
Text:
Ahahahaha! {0} wants help from me?
That's funny. Watching you act so recklessly is amusing.
You'll get no help from me.

Name: t_skill_dogeza
Text:
Hah, {0}. You really know no shame.
Did you really think you'd be forgiven?
Go on, kiss the floor! Harder!

Name: t_personal
Text:
What...? Have you come to gloat over my mistakes?
Hah, that's why I dislike you. Sure, I made a mistake, but you aren't one to talk.
Are you here to punish me somehow? Hah!

Name: t_personal
Text:
Ahahahaha, you've really screwed up now, {0}.
Do you want to know why?
By letting me live! Ahahahaha!

Name: t_personal
Text:
Have you come to grovel and beg for forgiveness...?
It doesn't matter. You will receive none.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I'm fully aware that you're human.
I just don't yet know if you're intelligent enough to be called one.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Hmph... You seem relaxed.
I wouldn't let you live if I were Gnosia.

Name: t_personal
Text:
{0}... Unlike you, I'm busy.
All I can really do for you is to try to guess what will happen next.
Maybe LeVi could help you out a bit.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Haha, coming to see me was a smart move.
Maybe you aren't as dumb as I had thought?

Name: t_personal
Text:
Just what would I get from talking to you?
Your friendship? Haha.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Go back, {0}.
I have nothing to say to you.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I wonder who will be eliminated tonight?
I'll be looking forward to seeing whom you choose, {0}.

Name: t_personal
Text:
We may have formed an alliance, sure.
But I'll cut you off if you hold me back, so be careful.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Open the land, open the land. Hah. All I see if cinnamon.
Why not get some hair on your chest?

Name: t_personal
Text: Hey, so the dead walk, and they come to me, huh?

Name: t_personal
Text:
You look bored. Why not help me with my research?
Hand me that... no, not that one...
No, the one next to it...! NO, not THAT one! Ah, never mind, just leave!

Name: t_personal
Text:
Could it be...? No...
You don't actually think your time is as valuable as mine, do you?

Name: t_personal
Text:
I really feel the vastness of the universe now.
To think that someone as unpleasant as you could exist here...

Name: t_personal
Text:
We simply need to weed out and destroy the fake, right?
Hah, that's so simple, it's stupid. Let's hurry up and get started.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Well, I don't have many other options, I guess.
You'll do for now.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Haha, lucky you, {0}. You're pretty fortunate, you know.
Acquiring a collaborator like myself.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Of course.
Do you even need to ask...?

Name: t_personal
Text:
From here on out, just act as instructed.
Doubt those I point out, and vote for them, that's all.
Haha, even you could do this, right?

Name: t_personal
Text:
I have to admit, I do have my regrets...
I regret underestimating the depths of your utter stupidity.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I can't believe I sought to collaborate with the likes of you.
I should thank you for helping me notice my own poor judgment.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I have nothing to thank you for.
Get out.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Hey, {0}. Should you really be playing around in a place like this?
Have you decided who will be eliminated tonight?
Of course not. Of course you haven't.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I did some thinking for you myself.
This time, we should get rid of {1}.
It's the obvious choice, considering the circumstances.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I'll let you decide, though.
Just remember that I proposed {1}.
Got it...? {1}, OK?

Name: t_personal
Text:
(OK...
Victory is finally coming within reach.)

Name: t_personal
Text:
(You understand, don't you?
You just have to do as I say.)

Name: t_personal
Text:
So it seems I've won.
Or rather, we've won, I guess...

Name: t_personal
Text:
{0}, you, too, proved useful.
I learned something from you.

Name: t_personal
Text:
You need to use vermin to get rid of vermin.
Haha, right?

Name: t_personal
Text:
So, a win for the humans.
Haha, do you expect me to congratulate you or something?

Name: t_personal
Text:
Oh, is that it...? Hmph...
I had thought you were pretty suspicious, {0}.
It's unfortunate I was wrong.

Name: t_personal
Text:
I guess you're not Gnosia, just a normal, dodgy person then, right, {0}?
Haha, I'm not sure which is actually worse.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Well, I guess you tried your best, hm?
As well as you could, at least.

Name: t_personal
Text:
The more I think about it... Hehe.
If I were Gnosia, the results would've been the exact opposite.

Name: t_personal
Text:
You should be thankful.
For having me on the same side, that is.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Is that all? What a shame...
Well, we knew how it would end anyway, since I'm on the Gnosia side.
The humans actually didn't do so bad.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Ahahahaha How weak! Humans are SO weak!
I would've liked them to have tried a bit harder.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Ah, {0}. You seem to want something, hm?
Well, here you go. Good job, {0}. Nice work. Great.
Ahaha, is that good enough for you?

Name: t_personal
Text:
By the way, I could take over this ship anytime I please, you know.
Where I go, what I do - it's all up to me.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Haha, ahahahahaha! Gnosia forever!
I'm FREE!

Name: t_personal
Text:
OK, which solar system should we destroy next?
It's going to be fun, {0}!

Name: t_personal
Text:
What are you doing? Hurry up and get prepared.
I'm taking you with me, you know. Obviously.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Good work, {0}.
That will do.

Name: t_personal
Text:
A conclusion has been reached!
The Gnosia... no, I! I've won!
Hahaha, what a waste of effort!

Name: t_personal
Text:
So, this is the end.
Hehe, you're so lucky, {0}.

Name: t_personal
Text:
It's not every day one gets to observe the destruction of the universe.
Ahahaha, enjoy!

Name: t_personal
Text:
Ah, so you were an AC Follower after all, huh, {0}?
It figures. Exactly as I suspected.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Haha, congratulations! You're so fortunate, you know?
As Gnosia, I'll put you to good use from here on out!

Name: t_temp
Text:
Places high import on logic, is quick to cast
doubt even on close allies. Surprisingly playful,
often falsely claims various roles.
